---
import DealerHubLayout from '../../layouts/DealerHubLayout.astro';
---
<DealerHubLayout title="Dealer Onboarding Checklist | Pinnacle Sales" activeSection="Onboarding">

<h1>Dealer Onboarding Checklist</h1>
<p class="page-subtitle">Your roadmap from signed agreement to first order and beyond. Each phase builds on the last.</p>

<h2>Phase 1 — Account Setup (Week 1-2)</h2>
<ul class="checklist" id="phase1">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-1">✓</span><div><strong>Sign dealer agreement</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Complete and return the Pinnacle Sales dealer agreement for your selected brands.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-2">✓</span><div><strong>WW Wood account creation</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Submit credit application and tax exemption certificate. Pinnacle Sales initiates your WW Wood dealer account. Allow 3-5 business days.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-3">✓</span><div><strong>Receive 20/20 / ProKitchen design credentials</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Pinnacle Sales will coordinate your 20/20 Design or ProKitchen catalog access for Shiloh, Eclipse, and/or Aspect.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-4">✓</span><div><strong>Join dealer communication channels</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Get added to email distribution for product updates, price changes, promotions, and training invitations.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-5">✓</span><div><strong>Confirm territory and brand assignments</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Review your authorized brands, territory boundaries, and any exclusivity arrangements.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Phase 2 — Product Training (Week 2-4)</h2>
<ul class="checklist" id="phase2">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-6">✓</span><div><strong>Initial product training session</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">In-person or virtual deep-dive on your primary brands. Covers construction, finish options, pricing tiers, and competitive positioning.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-7">✓</span><div><strong>Review sample program</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Select door samples, finish chips, and display materials. Discuss Eclipse Merchandiser and/or Shiloh sample racks.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-8">✓</span><div><strong>20/20 / ProKitchen software training</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Hands-on session covering catalog navigation, quoting workflow, specification best practices, and common pitfalls.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-9">✓</span><div><strong>Ordering process walkthrough</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Complete review of the order-to-delivery process. See <a href="/dealer-hub/ordering">Ordering SOPs</a> for full documentation.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-10">✓</span><div><strong>Warranty & service orientation</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">How to handle claims, warranty forms, replacements, parts, and the escalation process. Shiloh/Eclipse: 10-year warranty. Aspect: 5-year warranty. See <a href="/dealer-hub/support">Support & Escalation</a>.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Phase 3 — Showroom & Marketing (Week 3-6)</h2>
<ul class="checklist" id="phase3">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-11">✓</span><div><strong>Showroom display plan</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Work with Pinnacle Sales to plan displays that match <a href="/dealer-hub/showroom">showroom standards</a>. Includes layout, signage, and sample positioning.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-12">✓</span><div><strong>Order samples & merchandising materials</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Place initial sample order for door styles, finish chips, hardware, and brand signage.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-13">✓</span><div><strong>Download marketing assets</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Access brand logos, lifestyle photography, social content, and brochure templates from the <a href="/dealer-hub/marketing">Marketing Kit</a>.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-14">✓</span><div><strong>Update your website</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Add brand logos, product descriptions, and links to manufacturer sites. Pinnacle Sales can provide SEO-optimized copy.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<h2>Phase 4 — First Order & Launch (Week 4-8)</h2>
<ul class="checklist" id="phase4">
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-15">✓</span><div><strong>Submit first project for review</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your first 3-4 projects require a pre-order review by Pinnacle Sales before submitting to WW Wood. We check for errors and optimize the order. After that, you're cleared to order independently with design reviews available as needed.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-16">✓</span><div><strong>Place first order</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Submit your first production order through the WW Wood portal. Pinnacle Sales monitors the order through delivery.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-17">✓</span><div><strong>Schedule 30-day check-in</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Your Pinnacle Sales rep will schedule a follow-up to review your experience, address any issues, and plan ongoing training.</span></div></li>
  <li><span class="check-box" data-key="ob-18">✓</span><div><strong>Join ongoing training program</strong><br><span style="color:var(--color-muted);font-size:0.88rem;">Enroll in recurring product updates, seasonal promotions, and advanced sales training sessions. See <a href="/dealer-hub/training">Training</a>.</span></div></li>
</ul>

<script is:inline>
  document.querySelectorAll('.check-box').forEach(function(box) {
    var key = box.getAttribute('data-key');
    if (localStorage.getItem('ps_' + key) === 'checked') {
      box.classList.add('checked');
    }
    box.addEventListener('click', function() {
      box.classList.toggle('checked');
      if (box.classList.contains('checked')) {
        localStorage.setItem('ps_' + key, 'checked');
      } else {
        localStorage.removeItem('ps_' + key);
      }
    });
  });
</script>

</DealerHubLayout>
